	   <tr><td colspan=2>It checks the cold resist in the same way a cold based spell checks cold resist.&nbsp;&nbsp;If you get a successful check, then for that round of meelee you have an 11/16 weapon, if you get an unsuccessful check, then it's 7/16.  If you head on down to Naggy's lair, this thing is pretty much an 11/16 all around, but if you're fighting ice giants, it's pretty much a 7/16 all around.  For the most part, given that you're fighting mobs that are dark blue most of the time, you'll probably get a successful check 3/4 of the time, making it effectively 10/16, though while high level raiding, you're often fighting mobs that can be a very high dark blue, or yellow or red, so you're looking at it being closer to a 8/16 probably.  Really you need to experiment with it and find out where it works and where it doesn't.<br>&nbsp;<br>Keleric Medicor<br>Dwarven Cleric, Leader of Peace by Force<br>Skeleric Expirator<br>Gnecromancer<br>Tunare </td></tr>
